1
00:00:05,750 --> 00:00:06,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya.</font>

2
00:00:06,960 --> 00:00:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Daddy.</font>

3
00:00:08,090 --> 00:00:12,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hello. Wasn't Nana-san supposed
 to pick Kaya-chan up today?</font>

4
00:00:12,750 --> 00:00:13,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, well...</font>

5
00:00:14,330 --> 00:00:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems her mother 
passed away last night.</font>

6
00:00:17,420 --> 00:00:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

7
00:00:20,850 --> 00:00:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She did?</font>

8
00:00:25,930 --> 00:00:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello. You've reached 
Hanamugi Kindergarten.</font>

9
00:00:29,470 --> 00:00:31,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, good evening.</font>

10
00:00:31,990 --> 00:00:33,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chie-sensei?</font>

11
00:00:34,350 --> 00:00:38,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, she is. I'll put her on the phone.
Please wait a moment.</font>

12
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan's aunt is on the phone.</font>

13
00:00:44,110 --> 00:00:47,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello. This is Hasumi speaking.</font>

14
00:00:47,140 --> 00:00:48,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's me, Nana.</i></font>

15
00:00:48,650 --> 00:00:51,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nana-san. Sorry for your loss.</font>

16
00:00:51,360 --> 00:01:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="11">{\an8}<font color="#0d0d0f">Ext.</font></font></b></font>

17
00:00:51,360 --> 00:01:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="11">{\an8}<font color="#0d0d0f">Select</font></font></b></font>

18
00:00:51,360 --> 00:01:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="11">{\an8}<font color="#0d0d0f">Hold</font></font></b></font>

19
00:00:51,360 --> 00:00:53,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Chie-sensei, I need to talk to you 
about something.</i></font>

20
00:00:54,580 --> 00:00:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

21
00:00:55,980 --> 00:00:59,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's complicated, so I'd prefer 
to discuss it in person.</i></font>

22
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:04,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please come to the main house 
of the Ebisumori family.</i></font>

23
00:01:04,010 --> 00:01:04,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

24
00:01:05,570 --> 00:01:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

25
00:01:20,850 --> 00:01:22,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font size="50">Kaya-chan Isn't Scary</font></font></font>

26
00:01:20,850 --> 00:01:22,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font size="50">Kaya-chan Isn't Scary</font></font></font>

27
00:01:21,730 --> 00:01:24,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font size="50">Kaya-chan Isn't Scary</font></font></font>

28
00:02:40,010 --> 00:02:43,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">Episode 11: Mommy's House Isn't Scary</font></b></font></font>

29
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:46,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#ea4bb2">Origami</font></b></font></font>

30
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:46,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14"><b><font color="#c85c46">Manabi-ya\h\h\h\h\hCrayons</font></b></font></font></font>

31
00:02:46,650 --> 00:02:48,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this one.</font>

32
00:02:48,180 --> 00:02:50,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I drew that!</font>

33
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. I really love this drawing
 you did, Kaya-chan.</font>

34
00:02:54,950 --> 00:02:58,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I thought it'd make your grandma
 happy if she could see it, too.</font>

35
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:01,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At her grave?</font>

36
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:01,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mm-hmm.</font>

37
00:03:02,390 --> 00:03:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the story we're going with,
 right, Nana-san?</font>

38
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

39
00:03:07,910 --> 00:03:10,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her father was exhausted,</font>

40
00:03:10,330 --> 00:03:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I told him I'd keep her for the day 
to visit her grandmother's grave.</font>

41
00:03:10,790 --> 00:03:16,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="12"><b><font color="#070405">I'm sleeping all day,
— Shizuo</font></b></font></font>

42
00:03:16,660 --> 00:03:17,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But that's an excuse.</i></font>

43
00:03:18,790 --> 00:03:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Which means we're going there 
for a different reason.</i></font>

44
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're here.</font>

45
00:03:32,270 --> 00:03:33,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is...</font>

46
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#352319">Ebisumori</font></b></font></font>

47
00:03:34,090 --> 00:03:36,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The main house of the Ebisumori family.</font>

48
00:03:38,130 --> 00:03:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Ebisumori family. Where 
Kaya-chan's mother grew up.</i></font>

49
00:03:45,790 --> 00:03:46,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Okay, but...</i></font>

50
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:49,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you guys doing here?!</font>

51
00:03:49,810 --> 00:03:55,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It concerns Kaya-sama. 
There's no way I'd miss it.</font>

52
00:03:55,120 --> 00:04:00,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It concerns Osamu-kun. 
There's no way I'd sit this one out.</font>

53
00:04:01,130 --> 00:04:04,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're at a sacred site, Master.</font>

54
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More like a forbidden zone.</font>

55
00:04:07,250 --> 00:04:09,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with these guys?</font>

56
00:04:12,830 --> 00:04:14,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you want them here?</font>

57
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get Namu-san, 
but Mob-san's a complete outsider.</font>

58
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:21,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look who's talking.</font>

59
00:04:22,580 --> 00:04:26,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems they also have 
a history with Kaya.</font>

60
00:04:23,090 --> 00:04:24,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Look what I made, Mobuo.</font>

61
00:04:26,620 --> 00:04:29,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, I guess that's true.</font>

62
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:28,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Do you like it?</font>

63
00:04:29,620 --> 00:04:31,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You're so talented.</font>

64
00:04:30,260 --> 00:04:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need all the help I can get right now.</font>

65
00:04:34,730 --> 00:04:35,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Help?</font>

66
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:40,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's convenient. 
So <i>now</i> you're turning to an outsider?</font>

67
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did seeing the way your mother died 
strike fear in you?</font>

68
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:45,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master.</font>

69
00:04:46,490 --> 00:04:48,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ebisumori Mutsu...</font>

70
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:50,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was murdered. Isn't that right?</font>

71
00:04:52,310 --> 00:04:55,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop! There's a child in the room.</font>

72
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:57,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems you're still as sharp as ever.</font>

73
00:04:59,070 --> 00:05:01,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taking that into account as well,</font>

74
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:07,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I invited you here to share everything. 
About the past and about what's to come.</font>

75
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way, please.</font>

76
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:13,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan, why don't you go play 
jump rope in the yard while we talk?</font>

77
00:05:14,030 --> 00:05:15,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

78
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:18,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care out there.</font>

79
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:21,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, is there anyone else here 
besides you, Nana-san?</font>

80
00:05:22,220 --> 00:05:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. It's just me here.</font>

81
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:28,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although there were a lot of comings 
and goings when my mother was in charge.</font>

82
00:05:28,300 --> 00:05:31,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exorcists aren't exactly
 popular these days.</font>

83
00:05:31,260 --> 00:05:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The current head is a shabby psychic who 
can't even fake it like the previous one.</font>

84
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:37,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, don't be so rude—</font>

85
00:05:37,860 --> 00:05:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's right. I don't have the kind of power
 my mother or Kaya does.</font>

86
00:05:43,170 --> 00:05:45,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The best I can do is a basic exorcism.</font>

87
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:48,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Really?</font>

88
00:05:50,090 --> 00:05:51,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that's fine.</font>

89
00:05:51,690 --> 00:05:56,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because in this day and age, no one has a
need for such dubious people as psychics.</font>

90
00:05:57,920 --> 00:06:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, even if we're no longer needed, 
we can't simply be done with either.</font>

91
00:06:04,150 --> 00:06:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's left here are the 
remnants of such an occupation.</font>

92
00:06:06,630 --> 00:06:07,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Snap! Snap!</font>

93
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is urgent.</font>

94
00:06:11,150 --> 00:06:14,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I will tell you everything 
about the forbidden ritual</font>

95
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:17,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">used to bring back the shrine maiden:</font>

96
00:06:17,220 --> 00:06:20,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Curse Gestation." 
It was never meant to come to light.</font>

97
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Curse Gestation.</i></font>

98
00:06:22,030 --> 00:06:26,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's the method she mentioned 
for intentionally producing psychics.</i></font>

99
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:31,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Curse Gestation requires one thing 
above all else: a pregnant woman.</font>

100
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:35,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ritual is performed by 
the Ebisumori woman herself.</font>

101
00:06:36,450 --> 00:06:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The father doesn't matter.
Nor does the fetus's sex.</font>

102
00:06:39,710 --> 00:06:45,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever it was originally, sorcery will 
turn it into a vessel of a shrine maiden.</font>

103
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:50,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, there's something that is 
required for the transformation to occur.</font>

104
00:06:51,260 --> 00:06:52,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

105
00:06:53,340 --> 00:06:56,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The umbilical cord. 
The cord attached to the naval.</font>

106
00:06:56,790 --> 00:07:00,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was believed the shrine maiden's power
 lay in the umbilical cord,</font>

107
00:07:00,740 --> 00:07:03,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so the mother ingests the cord itself.</font>

108
00:07:04,810 --> 00:07:09,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see! Perhaps it was inspired 
by customs like eating the placenta?</font>

109
00:07:11,770 --> 00:07:14,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, the theory was proved correct.</font>

110
00:07:15,390 --> 00:07:17,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fetus altered by Curse Gestation</font>

111
00:07:17,950 --> 00:07:23,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was said to grow stronger 
the longer it remained in the womb.</font>

112
00:07:24,490 --> 00:07:28,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was born prematurely, 
so my time in the womb was very short.</font>

113
00:07:28,500 --> 00:07:30,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why my transformation 
was very minimal.</font>

114
00:07:31,010 --> 00:07:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is how I became a shabby psychic.</font>

115
00:07:36,540 --> 00:07:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makes sense.</font>

116
00:07:38,710 --> 00:07:42,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Basically, you're just 
a weaker version of Mutsu.</font>

117
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And there's nothing you can do against 
the curse on the Ebisumori family.</font>

118
00:07:47,630 --> 00:07:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a joke. I don't know 
where you picked up that grudge,</font>

119
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:55,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you should clean up your own mess.</font>

120
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean? What curse?</font>

121
00:07:57,750 --> 00:08:02,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ebisumori Mutsu didn't die from illness, 
and certainly not from old age.</font>

122
00:08:03,250 --> 00:08:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was cursed by another human being 
who bears a grudge against the Ebisumoris.</font>

123
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What makes you say that?</font>

124
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That day, I went to see 
Ebisumori Mutsu about something.</font>

125
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:22,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she suddenly died 
right in front of me.</font>

126
00:08:23,140 --> 00:08:27,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That, in itself, doesn't matter to me. 
If anything, I felt liberated.</font>

127
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:31,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I might even get 
to throw a jab at her after she died.</font>

128
00:08:31,630 --> 00:08:37,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But her spirit didn't appear
right after her death.</font>

129
00:08:37,250 --> 00:08:39,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But how? That's impossible!</font>

130
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:43,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even when a person dies, their spirit 
doesn't vanish the moment they die!</font>

131
00:08:44,310 --> 00:08:46,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why Kyoko...</font>

132
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:50,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. It wouldn't have 
happened in a natural death.</font>

133
00:08:50,030 --> 00:08:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The only explanation 
is a human-cast curse.</font>

134
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:58,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Members of the Ebisumori family 
are cursed by someone</font>

135
00:08:58,980 --> 00:09:02,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who holds a deep grudge 
against the family.</font>

136
00:09:03,300 --> 00:09:06,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you know who that is, don't you...</font>

137
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ebisumori Nana?</font>

138
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're absolutely right, Ebisumori Namu.</font>

139
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b>{\an7}<font color="#22232c">Let every curse
 be laid upon</font></b></font></font>

140
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:25,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b>{\an7}<font color="#22232c">Ebisumori Mutsu</font></b></font></font>

141
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:27,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's...</i></font>

142
00:09:28,010 --> 00:09:31,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="15"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#ffffff">Let every curse 
be laid upon 
Ebisumori Nana</font></b></font></font></font>

143
00:09:28,010 --> 00:09:31,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>like what was written 
inside Kaya-chan's talisman.</i></font>

144
00:09:31,990 --> 00:09:36,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mine was just a novelty for a child. 
But what my mother had was real.</font>

145
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<b><font size="18"><font face="Impact"><font color="#ffffff"><font color="#ffffff">Let every curse be laid
upon Ebisumori Mutsu</font></font></font></font></b></font>

146
00:09:37,350 --> 00:09:41,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She died in my place.</font>

147
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one cursing us 
in order to wipe us out...</font>

148
00:09:53,040 --> 00:09:54,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is none other...</font>

149
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:57,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">than my little sister.</font>

150
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya's mother.</font>

151
00:10:04,730 --> 00:10:06,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ebisumori Mirai.</font>

152
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:14,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#e76092">Kaya-chan
<font size="22">\h\h\hIsn't</font></font></b></font></font></font>

153
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:14,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#e76092">Scary</font></b></font></font></font>

154
00:10:14,010 --> 00:10:19,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#e76092">Kaya-chan
<font size="22">\h\h\hIsn't</font></font></b></font></font></font>

155
00:10:14,010 --> 00:10:19,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#e76092">Scary</font></b></font></font></font>

156
00:10:19,010 --> 00:10:22,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">Little Sisters Aren't Scary?</font></b></font></font>

157
00:10:22,910 --> 00:10:24,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan's mother is the one...</font>

158
00:10:25,230 --> 00:10:26,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...who killed Mutsu-san?</font>

159
00:10:26,890 --> 00:10:28,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hold on a second!</font>

160
00:10:29,110 --> 00:10:33,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Crafting a curse strong enough 
to kill someone isn't so simple.</font>

161
00:10:33,610 --> 00:10:38,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<font size="32"><font color="#1e1a15">Nana</font></font></font></b></font>

162
00:10:33,610 --> 00:10:38,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<font size="32"><font color="#1e1a15">Mirai</font></font></font></b></font>

163
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:37,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Kaya-sama's mother 
was born an ordinary person.</font>

164
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way—</font>

165
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:40,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She can.</font>

166
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because...</font>

167
00:10:43,210 --> 00:10:45,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every younger sister</font>

168
00:10:45,290 --> 00:10:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">born into the Ebisumori family 
are destined to bear cursed objects.</font>

169
00:10:51,060 --> 00:10:52,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cursed objects?</font>

170
00:10:52,780 --> 00:10:55,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At times, they wipe out targets with ease.</font>

171
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:59,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Other times, they generate vast wealth
 when that power is sold.</font>

172
00:10:59,970 --> 00:11:01,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They are the core of the curse.</font>

173
00:11:01,990 --> 00:11:04,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The reason the Ebisumori family 
has grown so large,</font>

174
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:09,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and can live comfortably 
even as the spiritual trade declines</font>

175
00:11:06,730 --> 00:11:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#352319"><font size="20">Ebisumori</font></font></b></font></font>

176
00:11:09,740 --> 00:11:13,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is largely because of those cursed objects 
rather than the shrine maidens.</font>

177
00:11:14,490 --> 00:11:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's what's inside 
Kaya-chan's mother?</font>

178
00:11:17,330 --> 00:11:22,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, she is pregnant with a cursed object.</font>

179
00:11:25,640 --> 00:11:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That doesn't add up, though.</font>

180
00:11:27,530 --> 00:11:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that's the case, the Ebisumoris
 would cherish the younger sisters.</font>

181
00:11:30,780 --> 00:11:33,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They should be treated well.</font>

182
00:11:33,050 --> 00:11:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would one bear a grudge?</font>

183
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Allow me to explain from the beginning.</font>

184
00:11:40,990 --> 00:11:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

185
00:11:43,680 --> 00:11:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's she?</font>

186
00:11:50,610 --> 00:11:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have a big tummy. 
Is there a baby inside?</font>

187
00:11:55,110 --> 00:11:57,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I said earlier,</font>

188
00:11:57,090 --> 00:12:02,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in Curse Gestation, the fetus grows 
stronger the longer it's in the womb.</font>

189
00:12:08,530 --> 00:12:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The child born has no human form,</font>

190
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:15,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the broken vessel 
constantly releases curses.</font>

191
00:12:17,270 --> 00:12:21,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The thing devours the mother's life 
and tears through the womb to be born.</font>

192
00:12:22,940 --> 00:12:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a cursed infantlike being that brings 
death to the one the mother wished for.</font>

193
00:12:27,970 --> 00:12:29,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hiruko-no-kami. The Leech Child.</font>

194
00:12:45,230 --> 00:12:48,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In their attempt to create shrine maidens
 with greater power,</font>

195
00:12:49,500 --> 00:12:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hiruko-no-kami emerged 
from that desire,</font>

196
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:55,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">ultimately sealing 
the Ebisumori family's fate.</font>

197
00:12:57,350 --> 00:13:00,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The younger sisters 
were called "Ohara-sama"</font>

198
00:13:00,070 --> 00:13:02,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and brainwashed to bear cursed objects,</font>

199
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:05,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">sacrificing their lives 
in times of crisis.</font>

200
00:13:06,710 --> 00:13:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the last person 
to become an "Ohara-sama"</font>

201
00:13:10,500 --> 00:13:13,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was this woman: Ebisumori Yoshie.</font>

202
00:13:13,630 --> 00:13:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My mother's younger sister.</font>

203
00:13:15,230 --> 00:13:17,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I remember her.</font>

204
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:19,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I showed you a photo before.</font>

205
00:13:20,550 --> 00:13:22,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's the woman in this picture.</font>

206
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:28,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aunt Yoshie took great care of us.</font>

207
00:13:29,270 --> 00:13:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was cheerful and kind.</font>

208
00:13:31,950 --> 00:13:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mirai especially looked up 
to our aunt like a real mother,</font>

209
00:13:36,940 --> 00:13:40,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">since she didn't get
much attention from our mother.</font>

210
00:13:42,250 --> 00:13:43,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoshi-chan!</font>

211
00:13:43,950 --> 00:13:47,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Hi, Nana-chan and Mirai-chan.</font>

212
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:51,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your tummy's so big! Can I touch it?</font>

213
00:13:51,330 --> 00:13:52,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Mirai!</font>

214
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not?</font>

215
00:13:54,400 --> 00:14:00,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-Because Mom said you're not supposed
 to touch Ohara-sama's baby.</font>

216
00:14:00,980 --> 00:14:05,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know anything about that! 
Nobody tells me anything!</font>

217
00:14:05,960 --> 00:14:08,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't make such grim faces, you two.</font>

218
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:14,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure the baby will 
be happier if you smile.</font>

219
00:14:14,550 --> 00:14:17,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can touch my tummy. Just be gentle.</font>

220
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:18,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

221
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:22,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

222
00:14:22,670 --> 00:14:27,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Unlike me, who, as the shrine maiden, 
already knew about the Ohara-sama,</i></font>

223
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mirai never knew the truth about 
what happened to Aunt Yoshie in the end.</i></font>

224
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:35,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or that's what I thought.</font>

225
00:14:36,530 --> 00:14:37,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right up until that moment.</font>

226
00:14:38,830 --> 00:14:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure she's uncovered the truth 
about the Ebisumori family.</font>

227
00:14:47,870 --> 00:14:47,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial">{\an1}<font size="15"><b><font color="#040102">She's spending the day with your older sister</font></b></font></font></font>

228
00:14:47,910 --> 00:14:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial">{\an1}<font size="15"><b><font color="#040102">She's spending the day with your older sister</font></b></font></font></font>

229
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:49,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial">{\an1}<font size="15"><b><font color="#040102">She's spending the day with your older sister</font></b></font></font></font>

230
00:14:54,030 --> 00:14:57,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So Kaya's at the house.</font>

231
00:14:58,540 --> 00:15:02,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">The Ebisumori Family Isn't Scary?</font></b></font></font>

232
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Look, Nana-chan!</font>

233
00:15:03,140 --> 00:15:03,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

234
00:15:03,550 --> 00:15:06,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look what I found. Isn't it cute?</font>

235
00:15:07,680 --> 00:15:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mom!</font>

236
00:15:20,030 --> 00:15:25,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since birth, my mother and sister 
could see things I couldn't.</i></font>

237
00:15:26,150 --> 00:15:30,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no, no! It's my little bunny!</font>

238
00:15:32,160 --> 00:15:36,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most of the time, a possessed object 
can be disposed of in a ritual fire.</font>

239
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:39,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember that, Nana.</font>

240
00:15:40,170 --> 00:15:41,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

241
00:15:41,990 --> 00:15:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I couldn't understand a word 
of what they were talking about.</i></font>

242
00:15:51,430 --> 00:15:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mirai-chan.</font>

243
00:15:54,330 --> 00:15:57,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the matter? 
Did you have a fight with Nana-chan?</font>

244
00:15:57,650 --> 00:16:00,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or was it with your mother?</font>

245
00:16:01,750 --> 00:16:03,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both!</font>

246
00:16:03,350 --> 00:16:04,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, bummer.</font>

247
00:16:08,290 --> 00:16:10,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that can't be helped.</font>

248
00:16:11,070 --> 00:16:14,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nana-chan and your mother 
are shrine maidens, after all.</font>

249
00:16:14,880 --> 00:16:16,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shrine maidens?</font>

250
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:22,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A shrine maiden's power is special, 
and they do a lot for the family.</font>

251
00:16:22,630 --> 00:16:29,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The reason we can live so peacefully 
without hardship is all thanks to them.</font>

252
00:16:29,340 --> 00:16:32,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she burned my stuffed animal.</font>

253
00:16:32,500 --> 00:16:35,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you're still hung up on that, huh?</font>

254
00:16:35,790 --> 00:16:37,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then...</font>

255
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about I give you something better?</font>

