00:16:38,230 --> 00:16:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="10"><b><font color="#bf5359">Neri <font color="#786ab9">Neri <font color="#bf5359">Neri-<font color="#786ab9">ne
<font color="#bf5359">Mix <font color="#786ab9">until <font color="#bf5359">fluffy</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font></font></font>

289
00:16:39,980 --> 00:16:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, really?</font>

290
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just don't tell your mom
 and Nana-chan, okay?</font>

291
00:16:44,470 --> 00:16:46,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want some, too, Yoshi-chan?</font>

292
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, but I'm staying away 
from snacks for the baby.</font>

293
00:16:50,950 --> 00:16:52,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a good mom.</font>

294
00:16:52,470 --> 00:16:53,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

295
00:16:54,770 --> 00:16:59,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aunt Yoshie felt more like a mother to me
 than my own mother,</i></font>

296
00:16:59,750 --> 00:17:05,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and I was a little jealous of the baby
 she was about to give birth to.</i></font>

297
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:09,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="14"><font color="#4a4745">Funeral of
<font size="24">Ebisumori Yoshie-sama</font></font></font></b></font></font>

298
00:17:10,630 --> 00:17:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My mother said she died 
in a car accident.</i></font>

299
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:16,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's the baby?</font>

300
00:17:17,630 --> 00:17:20,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not here anymore.</font>

301
00:17:23,320 --> 00:17:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take that!</font>

302
00:17:24,170 --> 00:17:25,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Begone, evil spirits!</font>

303
00:17:28,380 --> 00:17:29,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What was that for?</font>

304
00:17:29,620 --> 00:17:33,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, c'mon. It's what 
your family always does.</font>

305
00:17:33,460 --> 00:17:36,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Namah Samanta. Om Kili Kili!</font>

306
00:17:36,870 --> 00:17:38,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bam!</font>

307
00:17:39,510 --> 00:17:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never done anything like that!</font>

308
00:17:42,010 --> 00:17:43,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Liar.</font>

309
00:17:43,290 --> 00:17:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My parents say your family's nothing but 
a bunch of fake psychics running a scam.</font>

310
00:17:51,780 --> 00:17:53,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't want to go to school?</font>

311
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bullied again, I see.</font>

